column2: SELECT TOP # p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, s.z AS RedShift, p.deVRad_r,  p.modelMag_u-extinction_u AS mag_u,  p.modelMag_g-extinction_g AS mag_g, p.modelMag_r-extinction_r AS mag_r, p.modelMag_i-extinction_i AS mag_i, p.modelMag_z-extinction_z AS mag_z FROM galaxy AS p JOIN dbo.fgetNearByObjEq(#, #,#) AS n ON p.objid=n.objid WHERE p.specObjID=s.specObjID AND p.specObjID<># AND p.modelMagErr_r BETWEEN # AND # AND s.z BETWEEN # AND # ORDER BY s.z
